程序包 android.car.watchdog

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    CarWatchdogManager.ResourceOveruseListener
    Listener to get resource overuse notifications.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    CarWatchdogManager
    CarWatchdogManager allows applications to collect latest system resource overuse statistics, add listener for resource overuse notifications, and update resource overuse configurations.
    CarWatchdogManager.CarWatchdogClientCallback
    CarWatchdogClientCallback is implemented by the clients which want to be health-checked by car watchdog server.
    IoOveruseAlertThreshold
    System-wide disk I/O overuse alert threshold.
    IoOveruseConfiguration
    Disk I/O overuse configuration for a component.
    IoOveruseConfiguration.Builder
    A builder for IoOveruseConfiguration
    IoOveruseStats
    Disk I/O overuse stats for a package.
    IoOveruseStats.Builder
    A builder for IoOveruseStats
    PackageKillableState
    Killable state for a package.
    PerStateBytes
    Number of bytes attributed to each application or system state.
    ResourceOveruseConfiguration
    Resource overuse configuration for a component.
    ResourceOveruseConfiguration.Builder
    A builder for ResourceOveruseConfiguration
    ResourceOveruseStats
    Resource overuse stats for a package.
    ResourceOveruseStats.Builder
    A builder for ResourceOveruseStats
